text: The Samsung Galaxy S23, Samsung Galaxy S23+ and Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra is a series of smartphones in the Galaxy S series lineup by Samsung. They are Android based smartphones and phablets made by Samsung. It was succeeded by the Galaxy S24 series. Samsung Galaxy S23, Samsung Galaxy S23+ and Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra was began on 17 February 2023. == Related pages == *Samsung Galaxy S24 == References == == Other websites == *Samsung Galaxy S23 and S23+ *Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra Category:Samsung Galaxy Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2023
